1. Press **DISP/BACK** and select **START TRANSFER**. The selected items will be uploaded to Frame.io.

   !Start Transfer Menu

## Filtering Items/Choosing a Slot

To switch to the memory card in the other slot or display only items that meet selected criteria, press **DISP/BACK** in the selection dialog.

- To display only items that meet selected criteria, choose **FILTERING**.
- To switch to the memory card in the other slot, choose **SWITCH MEMORY CARD SLOT**.

   !Filtering and Slot Selection Menu

> ⚠️ **Note:**  
> Switching slots or changing the filter criteria removes any existing upload marking.

- Image transfer orders can contain a maximum of 9999 items.
- If **ON** is selected for **Frame.io Camera to Cloud > IMAGE TRANSFER WHILE POWER OFF**, upload will continue even while the camera is off.
